flowchart TD

    %% =========================
    %% ADMIN FLOW
    %% =========================
    A1[Admin opens Scoreboards page] --> A2[System shows all scoreboards]
    A2 --> A3{Admin action}

    A3 -->|Create new scoreboard| A4[Create scoreboard]
    A3 -->|Open existing scoreboard| A5[Open scoreboard builder]

    A4 --> A5

    A5 --> A6[Builder loads]
    A6 --> A7[Left panel: question list]
    A6 --> A8[Center panel: question preview/editor]
    A6 --> A9[Right panel: Question tab + Answers tab]

    A7 --> A10{Admin clicks Add Question?}
    A10 -->|Yes| A11[Create new question]
    A11 --> A12[New question becomes next screen]
    A12 --> A8

    A8 --> A13[Admin edits question text directly]
    A9 --> A14[Admin configures question settings]
    A9 --> A15[Admin configures answers/options]

    A14 --> A16{Question settings include}
    A16 --> A17[Show instruction]
    A16 --> A18[Required]
    A16 --> A19[Randomize answers order]
    A16 --> A20[Question-level jump]
    A16 --> A21[Type-specific config]

    A15 --> A22{Answer settings include}
    A22 --> A23[Answer label/value]
    A22 --> A24[Scoring toggle]
    A22 --> A25[If scoring ON show score input]
    A22 --> A26[Jump toggle]
    A22 --> A27[If jump ON show target question dropdown]

    A5 --> A28[Admin edits scoreboard design]
    A28 --> A29{Design settings}
    A29 --> A30[Logo]
    A29 --> A31[Logo max width]
    A29 --> A32[Logo alignment]
    A29 --> A33[Logo link]
    A29 --> A34[Header position]
    A29 --> A35[Section background]
    A29 --> A36[Top margin]
    A29 --> A37[Bottom margin]
    A29 --> A38[Footer content]

    A5 --> A39[Admin saves scoreboard]

    %% =========================
    %% STUDENT FLOW
    %% =========================
    S1[Student opens available scoreboard] --> S2[Create attempt]
    S2 --> S3[Load first question]
    S3 --> S4{Question type}

    S4 -->|info_screen| S5[Show information only]
    S5 --> S6[No answer stored]
    S6 --> S7[Move to next question or jump target]

    S4 -->|yes_no_maybe| S8[Student selects Yes / No / Maybe]
    S4 -->|multiple choice| S9[Student selects one or many options]
    S4 -->|radio buttons| S10[Student selects one option]
    S4 -->|sliding or linear or divided scale| S11[Student selects scale value]
    S4 -->|numeric| S12[Student enters numeric value]
    S4 -->|open_text| S13[Student enters text]
    S4 -->|image_button| S14[Student selects image option]

    S8 --> S15[Store answer]
    S9 --> S15
    S10 --> S15
    S11 --> S15
    S12 --> S15
    S13 --> S15
    S14 --> S15

    S15 --> S16[Calculate score contribution if applicable]

    S16 --> S17{Answer-level jump exists?}
    S17 -->|Yes| S18[Jump to target question]
    S17 -->|No| S19{Question-level jump exists?}
    S19 -->|Yes| S20[Jump to target question]
    S19 -->|No| S21[Go to next question in order]

    S18 --> S22[Skip intervening questions]
    S20 --> S22
    S22 --> S23[Continue flow from jump target]

    S21 --> S23
    S23 --> S24{More questions?}
    S24 -->|Yes| S3
    S24 -->|No| S25[Submit attempt]

    S25 --> S26[Calculate total score]
    S26 --> S27[Resolve result range]
    S27 --> S28[Store result in attempt]
    S28 --> S29[Update assessment progress]
    S29 --> S30[Show final result]